b2ef0cf07e207cbe62a34edb69ac4700bd5a75d9924e6597595e69f0988772d833d6af882cfa40278c9efe4b042da2952f9b7276b3c80c4b015b0c1490782b59  0005-Disable-tests-for-aports-buildservers.patch
